OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1775315484
OL,3,CAircraft in deadly crash exceeded
OL,4,Cweight limit by more than 30kg
OL,6,FAn aircraft which crashed seconds
OL,7,Fafter take-off in Derbyshire, killing
OL,8,Ftwo people, was more than 30 kilograms
OL,9,Ftoo heavy, investigators have found.
OL,11,FThe Hoffmann H36 Dimona crashed at
OL,12,FDarley Moor racetrack near Ashbourne
OL,13,Fmoments after take-off on April 8,
OL,14,F2025, killing both its pilot, 66-year-
OL,15,Fold Edward Browne and passenger, 64-
OL,16,Fyear-old James Litchfield.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1775315484
OL,3,CAircraft in deadly crash exceeded
OL,4,Cweight limit by more than 30kg
OL,6,FThe accident happened during an
OL,7,Fintroductory flight experience which
OL,8,Fhad been bought for Mr Litchfield by a
OL,9,Ffamily member, the Air Accidents
OL,10,FInvestigation Branch (AAIB) said.
OL,12,FA report from investigators has found
OL,13,Fthat a few moments after take-off,
OL,14,Fwhile the Hoffmann H36 Dimona was at a
OL,15,Fvery low level, it was seen swaying
OL,16,Ffrom side to side before it fell
OL,17,Faround 100ft-150ft to the ground nose
OL,18,Ffirst.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1775315484
OL,3,CAircraft in deadly crash exceeded
OL,4,Cweight limit by more than 30kg
OL,6,FIn the newly-published report into the
OL,7,Fdisaster, the AAIB said: "The impact
OL,8,Fforces were unsurvivable for both
OL,9,Fpilot and passenger."
OL,11,FHowever, the investigation has not
OL,12,Fbeen able to determine why the
OL,13,Faircraft did not climb normally or why
OL,14,Fthe pilot - who had more than 17,000
OL,15,Fhours of flying experience - could not
OL,16,Fcarry out a successful forced landing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1775315484
OL,3,CAircraft in deadly crash exceeded
OL,4,Cweight limit by more than 30kg
OL,6,FThe AAIB said no technical issues that
OL,7,Fwould have limited the engine
OL,8,Fperformance were found, but a throttle
OL,9,Freduction could have been a
OL,10,Fpossibility.
OL,12,FInvestigations into the circumstances
OL,13,Fof the crash uncovered that no weight
OL,14,For balance calculations were made by
OL,15,Fthe pilot on the day of the incident
OL,16,Fand the daily inspection book had not
OL,17,Fbeen signed ahead of the day's flight
OL,18,Feither.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1775315484
OL,3,CAircraft in deadly crash exceeded
OL,4,Cweight limit by more than 30kg
OL,6,FThe aircraft had a maximum payload of
OL,7,F170.6kg, though an error in its most
OL,8,Frecent weighing report stated the
OL,9,Flimit was at 184kg.
OL,11,FDuring the investigation, the AAIB
OL,12,Ffound that the aircraft's payload
OL,13,Fduring the fatal accident flight was
OL,14,Fapproximately 206kg - nearly 36kg
OL,15,Fheavier than it should have been.
OL,17,FThis has been classed as a
OL,18,F"contributory" factor into the crash.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1775315484
OL,3,CAircraft in deadly crash exceeded
OL,4,Cweight limit by more than 30kg
OL,6,FSafety action at the operating club
OL,7,Fhas been taken in the wake of the
OL,8,Fcrash, with the club amending its
OL,9,Fflight booking process. This means
OL,10,Fthose wanting to book a flight have to
OL,11,Fcomplete a flight waiver form and fill
OL,12,Fin data online, and their weight will
OL,13,Fbe checked before the flights.
OL,15,FThe British Gliding Association has
OL,16,Falso written to its member clubs
OL,17,Fhighlighting the importance of flight
OL,18,Fpreparation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1775315484
OL,3,CAircraft in deadly crash exceeded
OL,4,Cweight limit by more than 30kg
OL,6,FThe Association also plans to issue a
OL,7,Fnotice to its inspectors highlighting
OL,8,Fthe need to identify all relevant
OL,9,Finformation when producing weighing
OL,10,Freports.
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/7
